    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Goldenheart</i> is an old-school fantasy adventure with an unforgettable story and a surreal fantasy setting like no other. Play as an outsider, learning the ancient lore of a foreign land as you unravel the otherworldly mystery that has befallen it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002500/extras/532ffda9ad0c07f09d9081ac5ea9bb7f.poster.avif?t=1760654657\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002500/extras/532ffda9ad0c07f09d9081ac5ea9bb7f.webm?t=1760654657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002500/extras/532ffda9ad0c07f09d9081ac5ea9bb7f.mp4?t=1760654657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve environmental puzzles and fight monsters in real-time using targeting, dodging, and a shield. Manage your quiver capacity and stamina while encountering dozens of unique enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002500/extras/9e47c850d54452058669b37b589c33a2.poster.avif?t=1760654657\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002500/extras/9e47c850d54452058669b37b589c33a2.webm?t=1760654657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002500/extras/9e47c850d54452058669b37b589c33a2.mp4?t=1760654657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore and observe your surroundings in order to navigate the world without a map or quest log. Gain improved gear, but not experience points or levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002500/extras/59c2075f866f66d0044b205ba25b71c2.poster.avif?t=1760654657\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002500/extras/59c2075f866f66d0044b205ba25b71c2.webm?t=1760654657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002500/extras/59c2075f866f66d0044b205ba25b71c2.mp4?t=1760654657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Quick Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feature length action-adventure RPG in the old-school spirit</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Story driven with all original lore</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Xbox controller recommended but not required</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Three combat difficulty settings</p></li></ul>",
